  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is a two-part small scale, open-label, pilot study to evaluate feasibility and
      proof-of-concept for a respiratory assist medical device. The study population will consist
      of severe Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
