  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        1. Moderate to severe COPD (by ATS criteria)

          1. FEV1/FVC &lt;0.70

          2. FEV1 &lt; 60% Predicted

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Physical limitation that prevents walking for 6 minutes (e.g. lower extremity
             amputation, arthritis limiting function, significant angina, etc…)

          2. Lung pathology not explained by COPD, which may limit functional capacity (e.g.
             pulmonary fibrosis, malignancy, history of lung reduction surgery, etc…)

          3. Pregnancy

          4. Age &lt;18
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
